# Service-Oriented Data Access

Frontend apps must access data through service APIs, not directly through any database or storage backend.

Follow the full rule defined in `../haderach-platform/.cursor/rules/service-oriented-data-access.mdc`.

**Note:** This app currently reads from Firestore directly via the Firebase client SDK. This is acknowledged tech debt — do not extend these patterns. New features should use the agent API endpoints.
